"```sql\nSELECT \n    (COUNT(CASE WHEN alignment.alignment = 'Neutral' THEN 1 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(superhero.id)) AS percentage_neutral,\n    COUNT(CASE WHEN alignment.alignment = 'Neutral' AND publisher.publisher_name = 'Marvel Comics' THEN 1 END) AS marvel_neutral\nFROM \n    superhero\nINNER JOIN \n    alignment ON superhero.alignment_id = alignment.id\nINNER JOIN \n    publisher ON superhero.publisher_id = publisher.id;\n```"